<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8307203>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Pauridia aemulans. A, whole plant; B, leaf in transverse section; C, scape apex, bract and pedicel; D, individual flower; E, outer and inner stamens in dorsal view on right and left respectively; F, style and stigma branches; G, ovary in transverse section; H, capsule; I, seed. Scale bar A = 10 mm; B, H = 0.4 mm; C–G = 2 mm. Drawn by Nicci Page-Cairns from Hall 2645 (NBG!)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8307203/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8307269>
    dc:description "FIGURE 13. Distribution map for Pauridia pudica (triangles) and P. trifurcillata (dots) both from Eastern Cape and P. aemulans (squares) from Western Cape, South Africa." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8307269/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

